name: Virtuous Woman
description:
Inspiration for design: "Who can find a virtuous wife? For her worth is far above rubies." Proverbs 31:10  


100% cotton tubular jersey
Double-needle bottom hem and sleeves. 
Shoulder-to-shoulder tape. 
Preshrunk to minimize shrinkage.
